---
export const prerender = true;
---

<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Come Lavoro · Marco Munich Dev</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --bg: #141C1F;
      --bg-card: #1A2225;
      --border: #243035;
      --text: #E2DED6;
      --text-muted: #8A9699;
      --primary: #C17F3A;
      --primary-hover: #D4944D;
      --accent: #C17F3A;
      --navbar-bg: rgba(20, 28, 31, 0.8);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] {
      --bg: #F5F0E8;
      --bg-card: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #EDE8DF;
      --text: #1E2B2F;
      --text-muted: #6B7B7F;
      --primary: #A0614A;
      --primary-hover: #8A5240;
      --accent: #A0614A;
      --navbar-bg: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.8);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── Navbar ── */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: var(--navbar-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .navbar-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      height: 64px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1.75rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      transition: color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-links a.active { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-links a.active::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 1px;
    }
    .theme-toggle {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .theme-toggle:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); }
    [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .icon-sun { display: none; }
    [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .icon-moon { display: inline; }
    [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .icon-sun { display: inline; }
    [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .icon-moon { display: none; }
    .nav-toggle {
      display: none;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
    .nav-toggle span {
      display: block;
      width: 22px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--text);
      margin: 5px 0;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10rem 2rem 4rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.15;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 550px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    /* ── Timeline ── */
    .timeline-section {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 2rem 4rem;
    }
    .timeline {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 3.5rem;
    }
    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 1.1rem;
      top: 0.5rem;
      bottom: 0.5rem;
      width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary), var(--primary) 80%, transparent);
    }
    .step {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .step-number {
      position: absolute;
      left: -3.5rem;
      top: 0;
      width: 2.25rem;
      height: 2.25rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .step h3 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .step p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    /* ── Vibe Coding Disclaimer ── */
    .vibe-disclaimer {
      max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem 3rem;
    }
    .vd-inner {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .vd-tag {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .vd-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .vd-body {
      font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem; transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .vd-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .vd-col { border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .vd-col.no { background: rgba(180,60,60,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(180,60,60,0.15); }
    .vd-col.yes { background: rgba(60,160,90,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(60,160,90,0.15); }
    .vd-col-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; display: block;
    }
    .vd-col.no .vd-col-label { color: #c05050; }
    .vd-col.yes .vd-col-label { color: #3a9060; }
    .vd-col ul { list-style: none; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .vd-col ul li { padding: 0.3rem 0; }
    .vd-col.no ul li::before { content: '✕  '; color: #c05050; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .vd-col.yes ul li::before { content: '✓  '; color: #3a9060; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .vd-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      background: var(--primary-hover);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

    /* ── Mobile ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 64px; left: 0; right: 0;
        background: var(--navbar-bg);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        gap: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .nav-toggle { display: block; }
      .hero { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .timeline-section { padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <a href="/dev/" class="nav-logo">Marco Munich <span>&middot; Dev</span></a>
      <div class="nav-right">
        <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
          <li><a href="/dev/come-lavoro" class="active">Come Lavoro</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/vibe-coding">Vibe Coding</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/prezzi">Prezzi</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/blog/">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/contatti">Contatti</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="theme-toggle" id="theme-toggle" aria-label="Cambia tema">
          <span class="icon-sun">&#9728;</span>
          <span class="icon-moon">&#127769;</span>
        </button>
        <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Menu" id="navToggle">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Dal tuo bisogno al sito online.</h1>
    <p>Un processo semplice, trasparente, pensato per darti il controllo su ogni fase.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="vibe-disclaimer">
    <div class="vd-inner">
      <span class="vd-tag">Il mio metodo</span>
      <div class="vd-title">Costruisco siti con l'intelligenza artificiale.</div>
      <p class="vd-body">Non è un segreto e non è una scorciatoia. Gli strumenti AI mi permettono di costruire siti di qualità professionale in tempi rapidi e a costi accessibili, senza sacrificare la cura sul risultato finale. Lavoro più veloce, ma dedico quella velocità a capire meglio cosa serve alla tua attività e a perfezionare ogni dettaglio. Le demo nel portfolio sono tutte costruite così.</p>
      <p class="vd-body">Se hai visto qualcosa che ti ha convinto, possiamo parlare.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="timeline-section">
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">1</span>
        <h3>Ascolto</h3>
        <p>Parliamo di cosa ti serve, chi è il tuo pubblico e quali obiettivi hai, in una conversazione diretta che di solito dura meno di un'ora.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">2</span>
        <h3>Progettazione</h3>
        <p>Definisco struttura, navigazione e contenuti. Ti mostro un'anteprima prima di scrivere una riga di codice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">3</span>
        <h3>Sviluppo</h3>
        <p>Costruisco il sito con il mio metodo di vibe coding, con aggiornamenti regolari a ogni fase perché tu sappia sempre a che punto siamo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">4</span>
        <h3>Revisione</h3>
        <p>Lo guardi, lo provi, mi dici cosa cambiare, e le revisioni in questa fase sono incluse nel prezzo senza limiti.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">5</span>
        <h3>Online</h3>
        <p>Pubblichiamo il sito e ti spiego come gestirlo, con il codice sorgente e tutti i file che restano di tua proprietà.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">6</span>
        <h3>Supporto</h3>
        <p>Resto disponibile dopo la consegna per qualsiasi domanda o intervento, con un canale diretto sempre aperto.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <a href="/dev/contatti" class="cta-btn">Iniziamo &rarr;</a>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <a href="/">&larr; Torna a marcomunich.com</a>
  </footer>

  <script is:inline>
    const toggle = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');
    const html = document.documentElement;
    const saved = localStorage.getItem('dev-theme') || 'dark';
    html.setAttribute('data-theme', saved);
    toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const next = html.getAttribute('data-theme') === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
      html.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
      localStorage.setItem('dev-theme', next);
    });

    document.getElementById('navToggle')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.getElementById('navLinks')?.classList.toggle('open');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
